               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18400406-name-299" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18400406-name-299" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400406-name-299" type="surname" value="TILBY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400406-name-299" type="given" value="HENRY ILDEN"></interp>HENRY ILDEN TILBY</persName>
                  </hi>. I bought a flat, containing 27 lbs. weight of butter, in Newgate-street, on the 6th of March, and put it into my cart—I went into the market, and when I came back the basket and butter were gone.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18400406-name-300" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18400406-name-300" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400406-name-300" type="surname" value="BOLTER"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400406-name-300" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE BOLTER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am in the employ of Mr. Waite, of Butcher Hall-lane. I was at the top of Butcher Hall-lane and saw the prisoner take a basket out of the prosecutor's cart and run across the road with it—I gave information—we ran and took him with the butter.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
