                        <interp inst="t18400406-name-301" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES RAYNER</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Nelson-street, Shored itch. I was minding this cart, and went after the prisoner—I overtook him with this butter<lb></lb>flat, which was the one put into the cart—he had got half a mile from the cart, and was looking over the butter, to see what he had got.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> A man told me to stand by this, which I did, and I asked the officer to wait till the man came up, but he would not.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
